1
00:00:02,400 --> 00:00:04,330
Hey, what do you think of Akira?

2
00:00:04,330 --> 00:00:06,300
She's the most levelheaded
of the Three Great Water Fairies.

3
00:00:06,300 --> 00:00:08,570
She's organized, dependable, and takes charge.

4
00:00:08,770 --> 00:00:09,600
What's the matter?

5
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:11,540
Did something happen to Akira?

6
00:00:11,540 --> 00:00:13,780
Well, it's more like nothing...

7
00:00:13,780 --> 00:00:14,880
What do you mean by "nothing"?

8
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:15,410
You're really not making any sense.
What do you mean by "nothing"?

9
00:00:15,410 --> 00:00:16,340
You're really not making any sense.

10
00:00:16,340 --> 00:00:18,950
I guess so. It's not something
you two would understand.

11
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:20,410
Huh?
Huh?

12
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:29,820
"Dear Ai, it's been so warm here in Neo-Venezia
lately that I find myself breaking into a sweat."

13
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:31,890
"And also!"

14
00:00:31,890 --> 00:00:35,120
"Today, we changed uniforms!"

15
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,190
"That's right! We switched
into our summer clothes!"

16
00:00:38,930 --> 00:00:40,730
Oh yeah, Akari.

17
00:00:41,770 --> 00:00:44,900
I heard you worked on a traghetto recently?

18
00:00:45,010 --> 00:00:47,840
Yes, it was really fun.

19
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:51,300
After it was over, it motivated
me to work even harder.

20
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:54,180
I can't afford to lose to you!

21
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:56,940
You're both really motivated.

22
00:00:57,450 --> 00:01:02,220
Now that we've changed into our summer
uniforms, let's give it all we've got during practice!

23
00:01:02,220 --> 00:01:03,260
Okay!

24
00:01:03,260 --> 00:01:04,280
Roger.

25
00:01:12,870 --> 00:01:16,500
"I wish I could see you and the others
in your summer uniforms again."

26
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:22,470
"I'm sure they'll be a breath of fresh air
as Neo-Venezia changes seasons."

27
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:26,480
Oh my, Akari. Is that your summer uniform?

28
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:30,010
Yes! We switched our uniforms today!

29
00:01:39,630 --> 00:01:47,190
Do you remember that day
Oboeteimasuka ano hi o

30
00:01:50,810 --> 00:01:57,440
When your heart suddenly began to race
Futo kanjita tokimeki o

31
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:07,720
The rays from the blue sky were pouring over you...
Aoi hizashi abite

32
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:11,490
...as you cut through the wind
Kaze o kiru kimi ni

33
00:02:11,490 --> 00:02:19,030
I couldn't look away, and when our eyes met
Mitoreru to me ga atte

34
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:23,470
I couldn't help but smile
Egao koboreta

35
00:02:24,540 --> 00:02:28,840
It's just like a spiral
Marude supiraare

36
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:37,250
I want to spend my days waving to you
Itsumademo te o furitai hibi

37
00:02:38,650 --> 00:02:47,360
This is my proof that I was here with you
Koko ni tashika ni kimi to ita akashi

38
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:51,370
An eternal spiral
Zutto supiraare

39
00:02:51,370 --> 00:03:01,140
There's a path which stretches on ahead
Kono saki mo tsuzuiteru michi ga aru

40
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:09,980
When you climb the next hill,
Tsugi no saka o nobottara

41
00:03:10,290 --> 00:03:14,720
Let's meet again
Mata aimashou

42
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:21,590
That Keepsake Clover...

43
00:03:24,770 --> 00:03:30,030
I heard a really good bakery
opened around here somewhere...

44
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:30,470
Oh?

45
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:31,670
