Excuse me!

48
00:03:41,820 --> 00:03:45,020
Welcome! Our tomatoes are on sale today.

49
00:03:45,020 --> 00:03:47,820
Ah, no. That's not...

50
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,320
That voice!

51
00:04:42,210 --> 00:04:44,950
Her voice is wonderful, no matter
how many times you hear it.

52
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:45,310
