No sappy lines allowed! No sappy
lines allowed! Not allowed, Aika!

244
00:22:31,810 --> 00:22:34,940
No sappy lines allowed!!

245
00:22:35,420 --> 00:22:39,890
A shore awash in golden waves
Kin no nami kishibe ni

246
00:22:39,890 --> 00:22:46,550
Filled with yearning, I open my eyes and it's morning
Akogare mezameru no asa ni

247
00:22:49,330 --> 00:23:00,470
As my thoughts focus intently on someone,
Dareka no koto o tsuyoku omou toki

248
00:23:00,470 --> 00:23:09,350
Love rests on my palm, held high
Kakageta te no hira ni ai ga tomaru

